Feature: Calculator
  As an author of this article I want to demonstrate
  How to write a simple test using behave with a calculator as an example

  Scenario Outline: Add any two numbers
    Given I have entered <number1> into the calculator
    And I have also entered <number2> into the calculator
    When I press add
    Then the sum should be <result>

    Examples:
      | number1|  number2|  result|
      |       5|        2|       7|
      |       4|        8|      12|
      |     100|      200|     300|